HEADWORD: Gambadoes
<hw>Gam*ba"does</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[I. or Sp.
<ets>gamba</ets> leg. See <er>Gambol</er>, <pos>n.</pos>]</ety>
